How do I update this listing?




                                             Scoggin Management is based out of New York. Scoggin Management is a hedge fund  with  1-10 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $1,056,179,000 (Form ADV from 2016-10-01).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $599,712,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 59.61%. Scoggin Management's largest holding is Range Resources Corp. with shares held of 2,250,000.  Scoggin Management has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 31 13F filings in our database for Scoggin Management. 
                                           






